Simon & Schuster to Update Steve Jobs Biography, Will Release It On Time

-- B y   A n d y   F i x m e r
-- 
2011-08-25T01:22:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/simon-schuster-to-update-steve-jobs-biography-will-release-it-on-time.html
CBS Corp. (CBS) ’s Simon & Schuster book
publishing unit will update a coming biography of  Apple Inc. (AAPL)  Co-
founder Steve Jobs to include his resignation as chief executive
officer.  The release date for the book, written by former Time
magazine editor Walter Isaacson, will remain Nov. 21, Tracey
Guest, a spokeswoman for Simon & Schuster in New York, said
today in an e-mailed statement.  Jobs, who has been on a medical leave since January,
announced today he will resign as CEO. Apple’s board named the
56-year-old Jobs chairman, and said Chief Operating Officer Tim Cook will succeed him as CEO.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andy Fixmer in Los Angeles at 
 afixmer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anthony Palazzo at 
 apalazzo@bloomberg.net  